            This country banned plastic bags - should we?
            Kenya has the world's toughest ban on single-use plastic bags - you can be fined thousands of dollars or jailed for using them. The ban was introduced in 2017, so is it working?A film by Richard Kenny for BBC World Hacks. Like, Share, Engage.  
                
